data.description: Welcome to 235 Peters run! This beautiful home has 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths on a corner lot in a quiet cul-de-sac in beautiful Commercial point! You will find so much peace of mind being in walking distance to Teays Valley West Middle School and Scioto Elementary! With a very spacious backyard, 4ft wood fence, large deck area, and a 20x20 shed... You will have plenty of space to call home! The extended driveway adds room for additional parking or even space for an RV! Gas Furnace and AC replaced in 2019. Schedule your showing today or join us 10/20 & 10/22 for an open house!
